211: ```\n1212: \n1213: **CodeInterpreter example** (`examples/codeinterpreter.yaml`):\n1214: \n1215: ```yaml\n1216: apiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\n1217: kind: CodeInterpreter\n1218: metadata:\n1219:   name: python-interpreter\n1220:   namespace: agentcube\n1221: spec:\n1222:   authMode: \"picod\"\n1223:   maxSessionDuration: \"8h\"\n1224:   sessionTimeout: \"15m\"\n1225:   ports:\n1226:   - port: 8080\n1227:     protocol: \"HTTP\"\n1228:   template:\n1229:     spec:\n1230:       containers:\n1231:       - name: interpreter\n1232:         image: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/python-interpreter:latest\n1233:         resources:\n1234:           limits:\n1235:             cpu: \"1\"\n1236:             memory: \"1Gi\"\n1237:           requests:\n1238:             cpu: \"250m\"\n1239:             memory: \"256Mi\"\n1240:     warmPoolSize: 2\n1241: ```\n\n(End of file - total 1241 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# pkg/apis ‚Äî CRD AgentRuntime Type Definition Design\n\n## AR-001 ‚Äî CRD AgentRuntime Type Definition\n\n**Module**: `pkg/apis`  \n**Language**: Go  \n**Size**: S  \n**Purpose**: Define Kubernetes CRDs for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter resources, enable client-go generation, and provide type-safe API access.\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Package Structure\n\n```\npkg/apis/\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ runtime/\n‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ v1alpha1/\n‚îÇ       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ agentruntime_types.go   # AgentRuntime spec/status\n‚îÇ       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ codeinterpreter_types.go # CodeInterpreter spec/status\n‚îÇ       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ doc.go                   # Package documentation","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/deployment/design.md","time":{"start":1775863220362,"end":1775863220391}}}}
